(209, NULL, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 11px; line-height: 107%; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Read the text below then answer the questions.</strong></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 11px; line-height: 107%; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;<br></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 11px; line-height: 107%; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\"Maya\'s Quest: Unveiling the Hidden Garden\"</strong></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 11px; line-height: 107%; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong><br></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 11px; line-height: 107%; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">In the heart of a lively town nestled between rolling hills, lived a curious twelve-year-old named Maya. Her world was a vibrant tapestry of colors and sounds, a stark contrast to the tranquility of the surrounding nature. Every day, Maya embarked on a journey to the town\'s bustling market, where myriad vendors offered exotic goods from faraway lands.</span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 11px; line-height: 107%; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Maya\'s greatest fear was not the natural beauty that surrounded her but the peculiar alley where shadows danced with the fading sunlight. Legends whispered of mystical creatures that lurked in the narrow lanes. Maya, however, was determined to unravel the secrets that hid beneath the surface.</span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 11px; line-height: 107%; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">The bustling market was her gateway to a world beyond, and Maya relished the chance to explore it. She weaved through the labyrinth of stalls, her senses heightened by the eclectic mix of spices, the melodic tunes of street musicians, and the vibrant fabrics that adorned the shops.</span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 11px; line-height: 107%; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">One fateful day, Maya discovered an ancient book in a dusty corner of a quaint bookstore. Its pages whispered forgotten tales, and Maya\'s curiosity sparked like a flame. The book spoke of a hidden garden, a sanctuary of enchanting flora and fauna unknown to the ordinary eye. It was said to appear only to those with a heart brave enough to confront their deepest fears.</span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 11px; line-height: 107%; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">With newfound determination, Maya embarked on a quest to find the elusive garden. The journey took her through winding alleys, where shadows seemed to whisper secrets. Maya\'s heart raced as she confronted her fears, step by step, until she reached the mystical garden\'s entrance.</span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 11px; line-height: 107%; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">The hidden garden unveiled a world of wonders—a symphony of colors and fragrances that captivated Maya\'s senses. Exotic flowers with petals that glowed like embers greeted her, and butterflies danced in harmonious choreography. Maya marveled at the magic she had unveiled, her heart brimming with joy.</span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 11px; line-height: 107%; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; text-align: justi