(215, NULL, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 11px; line-height: 107%; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>Read the poem below <em>By Sylvia Evergreen </em>then answer the questions.</strong></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 11px; line-height: 107%; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Title: \"Harmony of the Wild\"</strong></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 11px; line-height: 107%; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><em>&nbsp;</em><br></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 11px; line-height: 107%; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><em style=\"font-size: 18px;\">By Sylvia Evergreen</em></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 11px; line-height: 107%; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><em>&nbsp;</em><br></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 11px; line-height: 107%; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><em style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Beneath the azure sky\'s embrace,</em></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 11px; line-height: 107%; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><em style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Where whispers weave through leaves like lace,</em></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 11px; line-height: 107%; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><em style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Nature, a symphony, pure and free,</em></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 11px; line-height: 107%; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><em style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Sings the ballad of eternity.</em></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 11px; line-height: 107%; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18