fic food <span style=\"background: yellow;\">commodities</span>.</span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"line-height: 115%; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;</span><br></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px;\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"line-height: 115%; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 18px;\">In conclusion, while climate change predates human existence, the Earth\'s average temperature has risen in the last two centuries. Many scientists attribute this change to human behavior, proposing that modifying certain activities can alleviate the impacts of climate change and global warming.</span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px;\"><strong><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"line-height: 115%; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 18px;\">Answer the following questions: </span></strong></p>', 1368);
