(301, NULL, '<p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><strong>Read the text below then answer the questions.</strong> </span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><strong>Nadia\'s Adventure</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"> Nadia was a curious and adventurous girl who loved exploring the world around her. One sunny morning, she decided to embark on a thrilling journey through the dense jungle near her village. Armed with her backpack and a sense of excitement, she set off on her expedition. </span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><br></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><br></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">As she delved deeper into the jungle, Nadia encountered various creatures and obstacles. She came across a mischievous monkey swinging from tree to tree. Although the monkey seemed playful, Nadia knew to be cautious around wild animals. She continued on her path, aware of potential threats.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><br></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><br></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"> After walking for a while, Nadia reached a wide river flowing with strong currents. She spotted a rickety bridge a little distance away. She hesitated for a moment, considering her options. The bridge looked old and unstable, but it seemed to be the only way across the river. Nadia took a deep breath, gathered her courage, and carefully crossed the bridge, ensuring each step was firm and steady. </span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><br></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><br></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">As she ventured further into the jungle, Nadia stumbled upon an ancient temple hidden amidst the trees. The temple was adorned with intricate carvings and mysterious symbols. Nadia couldn\'t resist the temptation to explore its secrets. She stepped inside, marveling at the grandeur of the temple and the stories it held within its walls. </span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><br></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><br></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">After a while, Nadia decided to head back to her village before it got dark. She retraced her steps, passing by the mischievous monkey and crossing the rickety bridge once again. As she emerged from the jungle, she couldn\'t help but feel a sense of accomplishment and wonder at the incredible adventure she had just experienced. </span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><br></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><br></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><br></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Among the logbooks, Nadia discovered a journal that seemed to belong to the ship\'s captain. The entries described a hidden treasure buried somewhere along the Australian coast. Her adventurous spirit ignited, Nadia decided to follow the clues in the journal, embarking on an exciting quest to uncover the lost treasure. </span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><br></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><br></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">The next few weeks were a whirlwind of exploration and adventure for Nadia. She followed the clues, traversed through dense forests, navigated treacherous terrains, and discovered hidden caves. The journey tested her resilience and determination, but her spirit remained undaunted.</span> </p>', 1396),
