(378, '4 friends: Zoya, Alice, Jenson, and Lloyd are all weighing themselves. Zoya is lighter than Alice but heavier than Jenson. Lloyd is the heaviest. Who is the 3rd heaviest?', NULL, 1584),
(379, NULL, 'Philips is an employee at a computer software company. The company has a unique system of rewards and training sessions for its employees based on the number of bugs they solve in a software each week. If an employee solves 7 or more bugs, they receive a bonus. If an employee solves less than 3 bugs, they are required to attend a training session in the following week. However, there is a 50/50 chance of no change in an employee\'s schedule for the next week if they attended a training session in the previous week.', 1585),
(380, 'Two friends, Natasha, and John are sewing clothes for a play. Natasha sews 3 costumes in 7 minutes while John sews 1 costume in 7 minutes. They need to sew 9 costumes together.', NULL, 1586),
(381, NULL, 'A tech start-up is looking to hire a new web developer and has received applications from three candidates: Sam, Alice, and James. They have the following qualifications: Sam: Has 15 years of experience and a Bachelor\'s degree in Computer Science. Alice: Has 3 years of experience and a Master\'s degree in Computer Science. James: Has 12 years of experience but no degree in Computer Science.', 1587),
