(1366, 'What is climate change, and how does it differ from daily weather fluctuations?', 'Climate change is short-term weather variations, unlike daily fluctuations.', 'Climate change refers to average weather conditions over time, distinct from daily changes.', 'Climate change is synonymous with daily weather changes.', 'Climate change is unrelated to weather patterns.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2', 'Climate change encompasses long-term alterations in average temperature and weather conditions, differing from short-term daily fluctuations.', 99, NULL, 0, 1),
